  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />We are hiring a <strong>Packer</strong> for a simple job in the West Area.<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br /><br />Label parcels clearly <br />Packing and sorting items <br />Assist in checking and preparing stocks for outgoing deliveries.<br />Keep the work area clean and organized<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>Able to follow simple instructions <br />Careful and detail-oriented <br />Physically fit and reliable <br />No experience required <br />Staff benefits <br /><br /><strong>Location:</strong> West Area<br /><strong>Contract:</strong> 1-Year Contract<br /><br />Interested parties:<br />Click ''<strong>APPLY</strong>\" or Send your resume to <strong>admin@psmanpower.com</strong><br /> with the subject line: “<strong>JRPT3133</strong> <strong>Application</strong>”</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br />By applying for this role, you consent to PS Manpower Pte Ltd<br />PDPA Data collected is strictly used for recruitment purposes only.</p>",
